# Accordion component

- Use the accordion component for expandable lists.
- The child of `AccordionItem` is the content to be hidden or expanded. 

## MultiActive

```jsx
<Accordion className="small-wrapper" allowMultiple defaultIndex={[1, 3]}>
      <AccordionItem title="Notifications">
        <div className="small-box" />
      </AccordionItem>
      <AccordionItem title="Setting">
        <div className="small-box" />
      </AccordionItem>
      <AccordionItem title="Connectivity">
        <div className="small-box" />
      </AccordionItem>
      <AccordionItem title="Integration">
        <div className="small-box" />
      </AccordionItem>
      <AccordionItem title="Assets">
        <div className="small-box" />
      </AccordionItem>
    </Accordion>
```

